column5: Anyone here interested in joining me on Erie for Bass Saturday morning?
When and where?  Wouldn't mind trying for some Erie bass for a change. I rarely specifically target them, and most days my little 14'er can't handle the big water.
Planning on launching at Crystal Beach about 6am, fishng till around noon...
Thats what this forum s all about   Nice of you to offer a seat, best of luck guys.
PigeonTroller,  Ill be at the launch same time hopefully. (14' starcraft, 20hp Merc)  Looking like the wind will be co operating with us for saturday!
